<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="One Mint Julep (Single Version)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="The Clovers"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Carol (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack)"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USAT20201136"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="36947818"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:24.900"><div begin="10.060" end="2:24.900"><p begin="10.060" end="14.090" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="10.060" end="10.220">One</span> <span begin="10.250" end="10.640">ear</span><span begin="10.640" end="10.700">ly</span> <span begin="10.840" end="11.410">mor</span><span begin="11.460" end="11.870">nin&apos;,</span> <span begin="12.370" end="12.480">a</span><span begin="12.480" end="12.540">s</span> <span begin="12.540" end="12.880">I</span> <span begin="12.900" end="13.010">wa</span><span begin="13.010" end="13.060">s</span> <span begin="13.110" end="13.590">wal</span><span begin="13.660" end="14.090">kin&apos;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">某天清晨，我正散着步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">某天清晨，我正散著步</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ある早朝 歩いていた時</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느 이른 아침 내가 걷고 있을 때</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un petit matin alors que je me promenais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una mañana temprano, mientras caminaba,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eines frühen Morgens, als ich spazieren ging</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Numa manhã cedo, enquanto eu caminhava</span></p><p begin="14.600" end="18.580" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.600" end="14.690">I</span> <span begin="14.770" end="15.170">me</span><span begin="15.170" end="15.220">t</span> <span begin="15.220" end="15.300">a</span> <span begin="15.350" end="15.890">wo</span><span begin="15.940" end="16.270">man,</span> <span begin="16.760" end="16.850">we</span> <span begin="16.890" end="16.940">s</span><span begin="17.000" end="17.390">tar</span><span begin="17.390" end="17.470">ted</span> <span begin="17.570" end="18.070">tal</span><span begin="18.150" end="18.580">kin&apos;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">遇见个女人，我们搭起了话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">遇見個女人，我們搭起了話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一人の女に出会い 話し始めた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">한 여자를 만나 이야기를 시작했지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai rencontré une femme et on a commencé à parler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Conocí a una mujer, empezamos a hablar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Traf ich eine Frau, wir kamen ins Gespräch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Conheci uma mulher, começamos a conversar</span></p><p begin="19.080" end="23.190" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.080" end="19.180">I</span> <span begin="19.280" end="19.560">too</span><span begin="19.690" end="19.740">k</span> <span begin="19.740" end="19.810">her</span> <span begin="19.840" end="20.280">home</span> <span begin="20.420" end="20.870">to</span> <span begin="21.580" end="21.950">get</span> <span begin="21.950" end="22.140">a</span> <span begin="22.140" end="22.630">few</span> <span begin="22.730" end="23.070">ni</span><span begin="23.070" end="23.190">ps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我带她回家想喝上几口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我帶她回家想喝上幾口</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">軽く一杯やろうと 彼女を家に連れて帰った</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">술 한잔하러 그녀를 집으로 데려갔지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je l&apos;ai ramenée chez moi pour boire un coup</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La llevé a casa para tomar unos tragos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich nahm sie mit nach Hause auf ein paar Schlückchen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Levei-a para casa para tomar uns goles</span></p><p begin="23.660" end="27.280" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.660" end="23.800">Bu</span><span begin="23.800" end="23.830">t</span> <span begin="23.830" end="24.210">all</span> <span begin="24.210" end="24.390">I</span> <span begin="24.410" end="24.890">had</span> <span begin="24.950" end="25.480">wa</span><span begin="25.480" end="25.540">s</span> <span begin="25.890" end="25.980">a</span> <span begin="26.030" end="26.450">min</span><span begin="26.450" end="26.520">t</span> <span begin="26.580" end="27.190">ju</span><span begin="27.190" end="27.280">lep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但我只有薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但我只有薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だが家にあったのは ミント・ジュレップだけ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 가진 건 민트 줄렙뿐이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais tout ce que j&apos;avais c&apos;était un mint julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero todo lo que tenía era un julepe de menta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber alles was ich hatte war ein Mint Julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas tudo o que eu tinha era um mint julep</span></p><p begin="27.550" end="34.560" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.550" end="28.200">One</span> <span begin="28.290" end="28.780">mint</span> <span begin="28.860" end="29.440">ju</span><span begin="29.440" end="29.720">le</span><span begin="29.790" end="29.870">p</span> <span begin="30.320" end="30.830">wa</span><span begin="30.830" end="30.900">s</span> <span begin="30.900" end="30.990">the</span> <span begin="31.060" end="31.440">cau</span><span begin="31.440" end="31.490">se</span> <span begin="31.490" end="31.620">of</span> <span begin="31.660" end="32.010">it</span> <span begin="32.050" end="34.560">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是这一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是這一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一杯のミント・ジュレップが 全ての発端だった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 한 잔이 이 모든 일의 원인이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep a été la cause de tout ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta fue la causa de todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep war die Ursache für alles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep foi a causa de tudo</span></p><p begin="37.140" end="41.140" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.140" end="37.230">I</span> <span begin="37.330" end="37.620">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="37.700" end="37.910">re</span><span begin="37.910" end="38.420">mem</span><span begin="38.490" end="38.850">ber</span> <span begin="39.050" end="39.460">ju</span><span begin="39.460" end="39.520">st</span> <span begin="39.640" end="39.950">how</span> <span begin="40.000" end="40.070">it</span> <span begin="40.110" end="40.150">s</span><span begin="40.220" end="40.760">tar</span><span begin="40.760" end="41.140">ted</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我记不清究竟是怎么开始的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我記不清究竟是怎麼開始的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">どう始まったのか 覚えていない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떻게 시작됐는지 기억나지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne me rappelle plus comment ça a commencé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No recuerdo exactamente cómo empezó</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich erinnere mich nicht genau wie es anfing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não me lembro bem como começou</span></p><p begin="41.720" end="45.630" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.720" end="41.900">Bu</span><span begin="41.900" end="41.930">t</span> <span begin="41.930" end="42.280">on</span><span begin="42.280" end="42.390">ly</span> <span begin="42.450" end="42.920">know</span> <span begin="42.980" end="43.390">i</span><span begin="43.390" end="43.490">s</span> <span begin="43.620" end="43.970">we</span> <span begin="44.100" end="44.460">should</span> <span begin="44.500" end="44.610">have</span> <span begin="44.710" end="45.320">par</span><span begin="45.320" end="45.630">ted</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只知道我们本该分道扬镳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只知道我們本該分道揚鑣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">分かっているのは 別れるべきだったということだけ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리가 헤어졌어야 했다는 것만 알 뿐이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais je sais seulement qu&apos;on aurait dû se séparer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero solo sé que debimos separarnos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weiß nur, wir hätten uns trennen sollen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas só sei que devíamos ter nos separado</span></p><p begin="46.210" end="50.200" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.210" end="46.290">I</span> <span begin="46.310" end="46.360">s</span><span begin="46.400" end="46.800">tole</span> <span begin="46.800" end="46.860">a</span> <span begin="46.940" end="47.530">kiss,</span> <span begin="47.900" end="48.590">and</span> <span begin="48.670" end="49.060">then</span> <span begin="49.060" end="49.140">a</span><span begin="49.240" end="49.750">no</span><span begin="49.790" end="50.200">ther</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我偷吻了一下，接着又是一下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我偷吻了一下，接著又是一下</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">キスを奪い そしてもう一度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몰래 입을 맞추고 또 맞췄지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai volé un baiser puis un autre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Robé un beso, y luego otro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich stahl einen Kuss, und dann noch einen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Roubei um beijo, e depois outro</span></p><p begin="50.730" end="54.390" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.730" end="50.830">I</span> <span begin="50.890" end="51.230">di</span><span begin="51.310" end="51.440">dn&apos;t</span> <span begin="51.470" end="51.920">mean</span> <span begin="52.030" end="52.400">to</span> <span begin="52.960" end="53.470">ta</span><span begin="53.580" end="53.600">ke</span> <span begin="53.600" end="53.650">it</span> <span begin="53.730" end="54.300">fur</span><span begin="54.300" end="54.390">ther</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我本无意得寸进尺</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我本無意得寸進尺</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">それ以上どうこうする つもりはなかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">더 진도를 나갈 생각은 없었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;avais pas l&apos;intention d&apos;aller plus loin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No tenía intención de llegar más lejos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich wollte nicht, dass es weiter geht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não tinha a intenção de ir mais longe</span></p><p begin="54.700" end="1:02.210" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.700" end="55.290">One</span> <span begin="55.460" end="55.950">mint</span> <span begin="56.020" end="56.600">ju</span><span begin="56.600" end="56.830">le</span><span begin="56.940" end="57.020">p</span> <span begin="57.470" end="58.000">wa</span><span begin="58.000" end="58.080">s</span> <span begin="58.080" end="58.170">the</span> <span begin="58.240" end="58.630">cau</span><span begin="58.630" end="58.670">se</span> <span begin="58.670" end="58.800">of</span> <span begin="58.840" end="59.150">it</span> <span begin="59.180" end="1:02.210">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是这一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是這一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一杯のミント・ジュレップが 全ての発端だった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 한 잔이 이 모든 일의 원인이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep a été la cause de tout ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta fue la causa de todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep war die Ursache für alles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep foi a causa de tudo</span></p><p begin="1:03.080" end="1:07.760" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.080" end="1:03.840">The</span> <span begin="1:03.870" end="1:04.110">ligh</span><span begin="1:04.180" end="1:04.240">ts</span> <span begin="1:04.310" end="1:04.430">were</span> <span begin="1:04.470" end="1:04.790">bur</span><span begin="1:04.840" end="1:05.010">ning</span> <span begin="1:05.030" end="1:05.980">low,</span> <span begin="1:06.490" end="1:06.750">there</span> <span begin="1:06.750" end="1:07.110">in</span> <span begin="1:07.110" end="1:07.170">the</span> <span begin="1:07.260" end="1:07.650">par</span><span begin="1:07.650" end="1:07.760">lor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">客厅里的灯光，昏暗摇曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">客廳裡的燈光，昏暗搖曳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">客間の明かりは 薄暗く灯っていた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">응접실의 불빛은 어둑어둑하게 타오르고 있었지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les lumières étaient basses là dans le salon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las luces brillaban tenues, allí en la sala</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Licht brannte schwach, dort im Wohnzimmer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As luzes estavam baixas, lá na sala de estar</span></p><p begin="1:07.820" end="1:12.350" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.820" end="1:08.340">When</span> <span begin="1:08.450" end="1:08.800">through</span> <span begin="1:08.800" end="1:08.910">the</span> <span begin="1:08.980" end="1:09.270">ki</span><span begin="1:09.330" end="1:09.490">tchen</span> <span begin="1:09.550" end="1:10.550">door,</span> <span begin="1:11.030" end="1:11.140">up</span> <span begin="1:11.240" end="1:11.430">po</span><span begin="1:11.530" end="1:11.600">ppe</span><span begin="1:11.600" end="1:11.640">d</span> <span begin="1:11.640" end="1:11.740">her</span> <span begin="1:11.800" end="1:12.180">fa</span><span begin="1:12.180" end="1:12.350">ther</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">她老爹穿过厨房门，突然窜出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">她老爹穿過廚房門，突然竄出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">その時キッチンのドアから 彼女の親父が飛び出してきた</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그때 부엌 문틈으로 그녀의 아버지가 불쑥 나타났어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand par la porte de la cuisine son père a surgi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando por la puerta de la cocina, apareció su padre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als durch die Küchentür, ihr Vater auftauchte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando pela porta da cozinha, apareceu o pai dela</span></p><p begin="1:12.390" end="1:16.760" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.390" end="1:12.830">He</span> <span begin="1:12.880" end="1:13.320">sai</span><span begin="1:13.320" end="1:13.360">d,</span> <span begin="1:13.360" end="1:13.410">&quot;I</span> <span begin="1:13.460" end="1:13.870">saw</span> <span begin="1:13.870" end="1:14.070">you</span> <span begin="1:14.070" end="1:14.870">when</span> <span begin="1:15.530" end="1:15.630">you</span> <span begin="1:15.710" end="1:15.890">ki</span><span begin="1:15.910" end="1:16.080">ssed</span> <span begin="1:16.080" end="1:16.250">my</span> <span begin="1:16.280" end="1:16.650">daugh</span><span begin="1:16.650" end="1:16.760">ter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他说，「我看见你亲了我女儿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他說，「我看見你親了我女兒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">彼は言った 「娘にキスしたのを見たぞ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그가 말하길 &quot;네가 내 딸에게 키스하는 걸 봤다</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il a dit « Je t&apos;ai vu quand tu as embrassé ma fille</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Él dijo, «Te vi cuando besaste a mi hija</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Er sagte, „Ich sah dich als du meine Tochter küsstest</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ele disse, «Eu te vi quando você beijou minha filha</span></p><p begin="1:16.810" end="1:21.370" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.810" end="1:17.180">Got</span> <span begin="1:17.230" end="1:17.400">to</span> <span begin="1:17.400" end="1:17.800">wed</span> <span begin="1:17.800" end="1:17.950">her</span> <span begin="1:17.950" end="1:18.420">right</span> <span begin="1:18.520" end="1:19.060">now,</span> <span begin="1:19.470" end="1:20.080">or</span> <span begin="1:20.240" end="1:20.540">fa</span><span begin="1:20.560" end="1:20.620">ce</span> <span begin="1:20.620" end="1:20.670">a</span> <span begin="1:20.690" end="1:20.760">s</span><span begin="1:20.790" end="1:21.180">laugh</span><span begin="1:21.180" end="1:21.370">ter!&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">马上娶她，不然就让你没命！」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">馬上娶她，不然就讓你沒命！」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">今すぐ結婚するか さもなくば命はないと思え」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금 당장 결혼하지 않으면 죽을 줄 알아라!&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois l&apos;épouser tout de suite ou faire face à un massacre »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Tienes que casarte con ella ahora mismo, o enfrentarte a una masacre!»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst sie sofort heiraten, oder es gibt ein Gemetzel!“</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tem que casar com ela agora, ou enfrentar um massacre!»</span></p><p begin="1:22.270" end="1:26.430" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:22.270" end="1:22.370">I</span> <span begin="1:22.470" end="1:22.770">di</span><span begin="1:22.880" end="1:23.050">dn&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:23.050" end="1:23.510">know</span> <span begin="1:23.610" end="1:23.970">ju</span><span begin="1:23.970" end="1:24.160">st</span> <span begin="1:24.650" end="1:24.740">what</span> <span begin="1:24.780" end="1:25.090">I</span> <span begin="1:25.130" end="1:25.230">wa</span><span begin="1:25.230" end="1:25.270">s</span> <span begin="1:25.350" end="1:25.920">do</span><span begin="1:25.920" end="1:26.430">ing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我不知道自己究竟在干什么</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我不知道自己究竟在幹什麼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">自分が何をしているのか 分からなかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 무슨 짓을 하고 있는지 몰랐어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne savais plus ce que je faisais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No sabía exactamente lo que estaba haciendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich wusste nicht genau was ich tat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não sabia bem o que estava fazendo</span></p><p begin="1:26.810" end="1:30.800" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.810" end="1:26.990">I</span> <span begin="1:27.010" end="1:27.260">had</span> <span begin="1:27.390" end="1:27.450">to</span> <span begin="1:27.580" end="1:28.160">mar</span><span begin="1:28.160" end="1:28.330">ry</span> <span begin="1:28.510" end="1:29.170">or</span> <span begin="1:29.290" end="1:29.710">fa</span><span begin="1:29.710" end="1:29.790">ce</span> <span begin="1:29.830" end="1:30.430">ru</span><span begin="1:30.430" end="1:30.800">in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我只能成婚否则死路一条</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我只能成婚否則死路一條</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">結婚するか 破滅するかしかなかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">결혼하지 않으면 파멸뿐이었지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je devais me marier ou faire face à la ruine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tenía que casarme o enfrentarme a la ruina</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich musste heiraten oder dem Ruin ins Auge blicken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tive que me casar ou enfrentar a ruína</span></p><p begin="1:31.350" end="1:35.280" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.350" end="1:31.410">A</span> <span begin="1:31.530" end="1:31.830">mint</span> <span begin="1:32.080" end="1:32.690">ju</span><span begin="1:32.690" end="1:32.900">lep,</span> <span begin="1:33.630" end="1:33.700">a</span> <span begin="1:33.800" end="1:34.160">mint</span> <span begin="1:34.340" end="1:34.940">ju</span><span begin="1:34.940" end="1:35.280">lep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普，一杯薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一杯薄荷茱莉普，一杯薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ミント・ジュレップ ミント・ジュレップ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 민트 줄렙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep un mint julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta, un julepe de menta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep, ein Mint Julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep, um mint julep</span></p><p begin="1:35.860" end="1:39.580" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:35.860" end="1:35.960">A</span> <span begin="1:36.040" end="1:36.410">mint</span> <span begin="1:36.600" end="1:37.200">ju</span><span begin="1:37.200" end="1:37.420">lep,</span> <span begin="1:38.120" end="1:38.180">a</span> <span begin="1:38.300" end="1:38.680">mint</span> <span begin="1:38.850" end="1:39.430">ju</span><span begin="1:39.430" end="1:39.580">lep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普，一杯薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一杯薄荷茱莉普，一杯薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ミント・ジュレップ ミント・ジュレップ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 민트 줄렙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep un mint julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta, un julepe de menta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep, ein Mint Julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep, um mint julep</span></p><p begin="1:39.820" end="1:47.150" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.820" end="1:40.460">One</span> <span begin="1:40.610" end="1:41.080">mint</span> <span begin="1:41.160" end="1:41.760">ju</span><span begin="1:41.760" end="1:42.010">le</span><span begin="1:42.100" end="1:42.180">p</span> <span begin="1:42.660" end="1:43.170">wa</span><span begin="1:43.170" end="1:43.240">s</span> <span begin="1:43.240" end="1:43.340">the</span> <span begin="1:43.390" end="1:43.780">cau</span><span begin="1:43.780" end="1:43.820">se</span> <span begin="1:43.820" end="1:43.960">of</span> <span begin="1:44.000" end="1:44.350">it</span> <span begin="1:44.380" end="1:47.150">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是这一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是這一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一杯のミント・ジュレップが 全ての発端だった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 한 잔이 이 모든 일의 원인이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep a été la cause de tout ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta fue la causa de todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep war die Ursache für alles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep foi a causa de tudo</span></p><p begin="1:48.260" end="1:52.920" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.260" end="1:48.760">I</span> <span begin="1:49.070" end="1:49.610">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:49.670" end="1:50.000">want</span> <span begin="1:50.060" end="1:50.150">to</span> <span begin="1:50.210" end="1:50.790">bore</span> <span begin="1:50.790" end="1:51.160">you</span> <span begin="1:51.660" end="1:52.010">wi</span><span begin="1:52.010" end="1:52.110">th</span> <span begin="1:52.200" end="1:52.350">my</span> <span begin="1:52.400" end="1:52.730">trou</span><span begin="1:52.770" end="1:52.880">ble</span><span begin="1:52.880" end="1:52.920">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我不想拿我的烦心事来惹你心烦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我不想拿我的煩心事來惹你心煩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">俺の苦労話で 退屈させたくはないが</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 고민으로 널 지루하게 하고 싶진 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne veux pas t&apos;ennuyer avec mes problèmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No quiero aburrirte con mis problemas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will dich nicht mit meinen Problemen langweilen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não quero te entediar com meus problemas</span></p><p begin="1:52.950" end="1:57.210" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.950" end="1:53.220">But</span> <span begin="1:53.300" end="1:53.500">from</span> <span begin="1:53.500" end="1:54.070">now</span> <span begin="1:54.070" end="1:54.600">on,</span> <span begin="1:54.630" end="1:55.120">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="1:55.170" end="1:55.520">be</span> <span begin="1:56.000" end="1:56.440">thin</span><span begin="1:56.500" end="1:56.660">kin&apos;</span> <span begin="1:56.710" end="1:57.050">dou</span><span begin="1:57.110" end="1:57.210">ble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但从今往后，我遇事定会三思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但從今往後，我遇事定會三思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これからは 慎重に行動しようと思う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 이제부터는 신중하게 생각할 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais à partir de maintenant je penserai pour deux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero de ahora en adelante, pensaré el doble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber von nun an, werde ich doppelt denken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas de agora em diante, vou pensar em dobro</span></p><p begin="1:57.250" end="2:01.970" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.250" end="1:57.700">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:57.790" end="1:58.380">through</span> <span begin="1:58.380" end="1:58.830">wi</span><span begin="1:58.830" end="1:58.910">th</span> <span begin="1:58.910" end="1:59.220">flir</span><span begin="1:59.220" end="1:59.370">tin&apos;</span> <span begin="1:59.470" end="1:59.850">and</span> <span begin="2:00.370" end="2:00.720">drin</span><span begin="2:00.860" end="2:01.020">kin&apos;</span> <span begin="2:01.070" end="2:01.370">whi</span><span begin="2:01.430" end="2:01.550">s</span><span begin="2:01.610" end="2:01.970">key</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我戒了风流，也戒了威士忌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我戒了風流，也戒了威士忌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">火遊びも ウイスキーももうたくさんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바람 피우는 것도 위스키 마시는 것도 끝이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;en ai fini de flirter et de boire du whisky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">He terminado con el coqueteo y de beber whisky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bin fertig mit Flirten und Whiskey trinken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acabei com a paquera e de beber uísque</span></p><p begin="2:01.420" end="2:06.560" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:01.420" end="2:01.560">I</span> <span begin="2:01.610" end="2:01.930">got</span> <span begin="2:02.090" end="2:02.490">si</span><span begin="2:02.490" end="2:02.580">x</span> <span begin="2:02.710" end="2:03.050">ex</span><span begin="2:03.050" end="2:03.160">tra</span> <span begin="2:03.210" end="2:03.580">chil</span><span begin="2:03.640" end="2:03.990">dren</span> <span begin="2:04.110" end="2:04.700">fro</span><span begin="2:04.700" end="2:04.750">m</span> <span begin="2:04.750" end="2:04.840">a-</span><span begin="2:04.900" end="2:05.220">get</span><span begin="2:05.260" end="2:05.380">tin&apos;</span> <span begin="2:05.410" end="2:05.830">fri</span><span begin="2:05.830" end="2:05.920">s</span><span begin="2:05.980" end="2:06.560">ky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就因为一时轻狂我多出了六个娃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就因為一時輕狂我多出了六個娃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">羽目を外したせいで 6人も子供ができちまった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">까불다가 아이가 여섯 명이나 더 생겨버렸으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai eu six enfants en plus pour avoir été trop joueur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tengo seis hijos extra por ponerme juguetón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich habe sechs zusätzliche Kinder vom Übermütigwerden